Class PhotoViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.PhotoViewController

  • public class PhotoViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the controller for the photo view. Photo view displays a photo's image along with its date modified and its caption, also a list of its tags.
    Author:
    Brian Schillaci
